<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Thank you</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style>
      /* Client-safe, inline-ish styles */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #f6f9fc;
        font-family:
          -apple-system,
          Segoe UI,
          Roboto,
          Helvetica,
          Arial,
          sans-serif;
        color: #1f2937;
      }
      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background: #f6f9fc;
        padding: 40px 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .header {
        background: #0f172a;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 120px;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto 12px;
      }
      .brand {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 28px 24px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: #111827;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }
      .card {
        background: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #eef2f7;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .meta {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #374151;
      }
      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: #eef2f7;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: #fff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .muted {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 18px;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        body {
          background: #0b1220;
          color: #e5e7eb;
        }
        .container {
          background: #0f172a;
          box-shadow: none;
        }
        .header {
          background: #0b1220;
        }
        h1,
        .meta {
          color: #e5e7eb;
        }
        .card {
          background: #111827;
          border-color: #1f2937;
        }
        .divider {
          background: #1f2937;
        }
        .footer {
          color: #9ca3af;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <img src="https://www.shrlbd.com/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
          <p class="brand">Smart Health Care & Research</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <h1>Thank you, <%= name %> üëã</h1>
          <p>
            Thank you for joining with us. We‚Äôve received your request and our team will review it
            shortly. We‚Äôll contact you as soon as possible with next steps.
          </p>

          <div class="card">
            <p class="meta"><strong>Summary of your submission</strong></p>
            <p class="meta">Email: <%= email %></p>
            <p class="meta">Phone: <%= phone %></p>
            <p class="meta">Organization: <%= organization %></p>
            <p class="meta">Occupation: <%= occupation %></p>
            <p class="meta">Area of Interest: <%= field_of_interest %></p>
            <p class="meta">Time Commitment: <%= time_commitment %></p>
          </div>

          <p>
            If you have anything to add or want to update your information, just reply to this
            email.
          </p>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <p>
            Meanwhile, you can visit our website to learn more about our programs and opportunities.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.shrlbd.com" class="button" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
              >Visit Our Website</a
            >
          </p>

          <p class="muted">This is an automated message, but replies are monitored by our team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          Smart HealthCare & Research Ltd. All rights reserved.<br />
          You‚Äôre receiving this because you submitted a ‚ÄúJoin Team‚Äù request.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
